---
title: Creamy Double Mustard Chicken Penne with Baby Leaves
description: Tonight, our favourite pasta is getting a thorough coating with a rich, Dijon-infused cream sauce. Toss through some juicy chicken and vibrant green leaves for a meal you won’t soon forget!

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with penne due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
